dct_title_s: Sinaloa / autores Agustín y Joaquín Palacios Roji García ; editor Joaquín Palacios Roji García.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Publisher's number: 24. On verso:Map  with text describing points of interest . Map shows international, state, and municipal boundaries, 4 classes of roads, railroads, national parks, archaeological sites, and Mountain Time zone boundary. "1 cm sobre el plano representa 8 km sobre el terreno".
